      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-3E7DD32D-7ADE-4748-A758-D94073803D65" signavio:alignment="left">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioDictionaryLink propertyId="name">
               <signavio:dictionaryLink>/glossary/99ed2fb6879346238999fda867d77df1</signavio:dictionaryLink>
            </signavio:signavioDictionaryLink>
            <signavio:signavioType dataObjectType="IT-System"/>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bgcolor" metaValue="#e1e1e1"/>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>SAP Extended Warehouse Management (EWM)</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-C7AC8373-424F-4861-B877-38503129AD25" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Storage Bin Determination includes Batch-managed , Temperature-controlled  and Hazardous Inventory </text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-79EF5E24-744E-47EA-950C-6D979BBB61E7" signavio:alignment="left">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioDictionaryLink propertyId="name">
               <signavio:dictionaryLink>/glossary/99ed2fb6879346238999fda867d77df1</signavio:dictionaryLink>
            </signavio:signavioDictionaryLink>
            <signavio:signavioType dataObjectType="IT-System"/>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bgcolor" metaValue="#e1e1e1"/>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
            <signavio:signavioLabel ref="text_name" valign="middle" x="44.0" y="73.0"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>SAP Extended Warehouse Management (EWM)</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-EB4361C5-157F-4387-9887-3619E01F5DC3" signavio:alignment="left">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioDictionaryLink propertyId="name">
               <signavio:dictionaryLink>/glossary/99ed2fb6879346238999fda867d77df1</signavio:dictionaryLink>
            </signavio:signavioDictionaryLink>
            <signavio:signavioType dataObjectType="IT-System"/>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bgcolor" metaValue="#e1e1e1"/>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>SAP Extended Warehouse Management (EWM)</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-4B054170-D8F2-4520-A0DF-D42A8413F965" signavio:alignment="left">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioDictionaryLink propertyId="name">
               <signavio:dictionaryLink>/glossary/99ed2fb6879346238999fda867d77df1</signavio:dictionaryLink>
            </signavio:signavioDictionaryLink>
            <signavio:signavioType dataObjectType="IT-System"/>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bgcolor" metaValue="#e1e1e1"/>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>SAP Extended Warehouse Management (EWM)</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-DBB4647D-1834-4C02-8A6A-55178692ECB1" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Based on Putaway Control Indicator and Storage Type Search Sequence</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-9D1F64A6-9839-4ABF-AF63-DED6647B2D3E" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Based on Storage Section Indicator and Storage Section Search Sequence</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-9F99F473-CC1B-42B2-9E58-CB9E71EBEE79" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>In this task, at  backend, if there are any limitations at Bin Type Level, those will be automatically considered by the system. 
For example, if the Bin has reached its capacity, system will give detailed error message and will not allow to create Putaway Task. It will only take the correct Storage Bin for Putaway.</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-E8B897C6-E289-4866-BB7E-234E4BC4FE6C" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Goods Receipt will act as  Putaway Label- Yet to be Finalized</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-9551E904-BD0A-40CC-96DE-7F2D491811A0" signavio:alignment="left">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioDictionaryLink propertyId="name">
               <signavio:dictionaryLink>/glossary/99ed2fb6879346238999fda867d77df1</signavio:dictionaryLink>
            </signavio:signavioDictionaryLink>
            <signavio:signavioType dataObjectType="IT-System"/>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bgcolor" metaValue="#e1e1e1"/>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>SAP Extended Warehouse Management (EWM)</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-A3D38154-1F0C-4BE1-A7A0-0AC9DE804146" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Putaway for Batch managed , Temperature Controlled, &amp; Hazardous Inventory </text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-B2F0F917-CCF6-43B3-9677-390CE0731FE5" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Hazardous Inventory have Special Handling Unit Characteristics</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-8EAB2306-A947-4338-B339-BDA31204E56F" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>SAP Monitor provides the Historical Details of the Storage Bin</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-319472FB-CD32-4F98-8D80-F2A3D47944F1" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Confirmation of Putaway Task and Exceptions during Putaway are captured in this L3.</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-B2593F56-2F77-4FFA-9180-545DC60CF92E" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Placeholder For Expedite Process
Yet to be finalized</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-406A6402-3131-410A-8A7C-ED01073998B1" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Placeholder for Copper Putaway Process -  Yet to be Finalized</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-7B07FC0C-C2A0-40DC-82CB-9532D7135C31" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>In this point, stock will not be visible to Factory or  Customers in S4 system
Stock Type of Goods will be F1- Unrestricted-Use in Putaway</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-1FDC8C89-E2F3-497B-BC2C-8EC882EE1F39" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>MQCS relevance will be checked from the (Supplier+ plant Custom Table )created in the S/4 system</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-F51911E3-9213-45E3-9A58-3868349E27A6" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Process Tower: Procure to Pay (PTP)
Process Group: L Logistics &amp; Inventory Management
Process Name: L-040-120 Determine Put-away Location</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-205FEC77-B77A-47BD-BFA3-F50E4FC8FC73" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Flow is Applicable to R3: 
Receiving from External Vendor Scenario :ASN and Non ASN Scenario 
Applicable Parts - Spares 
Intel Owned Inventory ,Supplier Consignment and Copper Shipments</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-93514669-3B2C-4FF1-B8EE-046A9856001F" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
            <signavio:signavioLabel bold="" fill="#ff0000" fontFamily="" fontSize="" italic="" ref="text-left"/>
            <signavio:signavioLabel bold="" fill="#ff0000" fontFamily="" fontSize="" italic="" ref="text-right"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Flow has been migrated to BIC. Please inform the process steward Johnson, Graeme &lt;graeme.johnson@intel.com&gt; and BPM Champions D'Elia, Traci &lt;traci.delia@intel.com&gt;,Newman, Jennifer &lt;jennifer.newman@intel.com&gt;of any design changes that occur within the flow moving forward. This will enable us to reflect those changes in the BIC and WIKI business process documentation.</text>
      </textAnnotation>
   </process>
   <bpmndi:BPMNDiagram id="sid-9ae5390f-6c91-4c43-8790-1dedc35ae967" name="L-040-120_Determine Put-away Location">
      <bpmndi:BPMNPlane bpmnElement="sid-907b5865-29cb-432c-a122-67d7b40c6d83" id="sid-dc4b8cd6-18e9-4574-85af-03b293b87e69">
